help: Shows help, can show help for a specific command too.
wp: This is the wp-cli util integration with the bot.
addresource: Add a cyber resource to the resources page on the website. Takes a name and then a link to add as arguments.
roll: Roll a Random number. First argument is the low number second is the high number. Will use a max signed WORD if you don't specify a max and 0 as a minimum if you don't specify a low.
